instructions: Put the dinner plate in the center of the table cloth
put the salad plate in the center of the dinner plate
put the napkin on the center of the salad plate with the napkin fold on the top portion
put the wine glass on the top right corner of the table cloth a couple inches from the edge
put the water glass on the table cloth to the lower right of the wine glass
put the salad fork on the far left center of the table cloth with the prong facing up
put the dinner fork directly to the right of the salad fork with the prong facing up
put the dinner knife directly to the right of the dinner plate with the blade facing up
put the soup spoon to the left of the dinner knife with the bowl facing up
